dc_description_s: This data represents trails for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2023. [GreenCircle is a vector representation of the Green Circle bicycle/pedestrian trail in Stevens Point, Wisconsin. Most of the trail was mapped using a resource grade GPS. The remainder is traced from airphotos. Recommended use scale is no larger than 1:2400.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
